OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunny spells leading
OL,7,Fto clear spells after sunset.
OL,8,FOvernight remaining dry with long
OL,9,Fclear spells for most, but turning
OL,10,Fcloudier in the west of Dumfries.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSunny spells to start but
OL,13,Fsoon turning cloudy through the
OL,14,Fmorning. A cloudy afternoon with rain
OL,15,Fpushing eastwards, heavy at times in
OL,16,Fthe west but more patchy in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
